Here, too, there are price and quality categories.
For some it may be unacceptable to spend for a reader 8,000 crowns, as well as a fan of Pink Floyd perhaps hardly digests the headphones from the twenty-crown market.
Two extremes between which there is enough space for everyone.
The choice is wide.
The decision is the battery life.
Some high-quality music players are able to do much more than just read music, but they don’t even do cell phones by mistake.
