In this sense, music readers (especially the simplest ones) are much more effective.
As for cheap mobile phones, don’t count that they can last for more than a few hours.
If you still add us, from time to time, some calls, get another charger at work for safety, this also applies to the most expensive appliances.
But you won’t have this problem with an MP3 player, even the worst ones last at least 9 hours at continuous functionality with a recharge.
Another problem occurs when you download music to your mobile phone.
Unfortunately, only a limited number of devices have a universal USB port and not all of them can be connected to the computer without special software.
